short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Quickly access your Github repos from your browser omnibox

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Quickly jump to any of your repos in Github by just typing in 'gh' and then hitting tab in the browser omnibox.

Github Repo Search extension will autocomplete suggestions based on the repositories you have access to. A valid Github token is needed in order to get access to your repositories.
